[SMG_CV X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="SMG"
FriendlyNamePlural="SMGs"
BriefSummary="Submachine guns offer a lighter, more concealable alternative to the standard assault rifle, although they lack the same punch and are less accurate at long range."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Firing the primary weapon ends the soldier's turn, in the absence of special training.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades recovered from ADVENT enemies to improve the SMG's tactical effectiveness. \n<Bullet/> SMG-style weapons offer bonus mobility, close-quarters accuracy and concealment relative to assault rifles, but they do less damage, have less ammo, and suffer accuracy penalties at long range."
AbilityDescName="SMG"

